00:01:05,310 --> 00:01:08,460
PATIENT PANDA, VEEFRIENDS, 2021

14
00:01:09,180 --> 00:01:12,660
VeeFriends is a Gary Vaynerchuk NFT project,

15
00:01:12,660 --> 00:01:17,490
comprised of 10,255 hand drawn characters.

16
00:01:17,940 --> 00:01:21,660
The project aims to create a meaningful community

17
00:01:21,660 --> 00:01:25,650
and real life value around intellectual property.

18
00:01:26,580 --> 00:01:29,760
They do this by adding utility to these tokens,

19
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:31,500
such as access to VeeCon

20
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:36,210
an annual conference that Mr. Vaynerchuk plans to produce for the next three years.

21
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:42,090
The VeeFriends collection was launched in May 2021 and by October 1st,

22
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:46,830
the original hand-drawn artworks made their Christie's debut,

23
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:49,860
resulting in a seven figure sale.

24
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:54,180
The collection of characters represent human traits

25
00:01:54,180 --> 00:02:00,030
that Mr. Vaynerchuk most admires and which he believes will lead to happiness and success.

26
00:02:00,810 --> 00:02:04,920
A portion of funds from token royalties will be donated to charities,

27
00:02:05,070 --> 00:02:07,890
as well as five free scholarship tokens

28
